# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# Aegis private translator (D-011 close — track stub, ignore impl)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# Public clones get the empty `rift-aegis` stub crate (Cargo.toml +
# src/lib.rs are TRACKED). The real implementation lives in
# additional gitignored .rs files alongside lib.rs (detect.rs,
# snapshot.rs, etc.). lib.rs cfg-gates `pub mod detect; pub mod
# snapshot; ...` behind the `private_modules` feature, which
# src-tauri's `aegis` feature enables. Public CI builds default
# features → private_modules off → stub compiles to empty crate
# without needing the private files. See DEFERRED.md C-014.
crates/rift-aegis/src/*
!crates/rift-aegis/src/lib.rs
crates/rift-aegis/target/
